playstore_details.description:
Dompet Bitcoin Indonesia is a bitcoin wallet that is fully integrated with Indodax.com. You can now easily access every feature that is available in Indodax.com website through your smartphones only with a few clicks of your fingers.

What can you do with Dompet Bitcoin Indonesia?

- Keep & send Bitcoins with user-friendly interface
- Instant & hassle-free Bitcoin-Rupiah trading
- Top up your Rupiah balance or withdraw it from your account
- Stylish price widget with customized alarm for your homescreen
- Easier login process to your Indodax account with customized PIN
- Analyze Bitcoin’s price movement through detailed live charts
- Chat with other members through our Chatroom
- Create & redeem Indodax vouchers
- Check your transaction history
- 24/7 Online Customer Support that can be accessed via Live Chat and E-mail

This mobile app is available both in English and Bahasa, based on your settings preferences and we are using two factor authentication via SMS Pin to keep your account secure. Download now and enjoy how easy it is to use and trade Bitcoin with our new app!

If you have any critics or suggestion, feel free to send us your feedback via e-mail to support@indodax.com Our developer team will be right with you.
